heet唔會公開編輯驚比人玩野）<br />\n會盡量每日更新<br />\n另附上食環舉報熱線 2868 0000或 1823 <br />\n<br />\nenquiries@fehd.gov.hk<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomments%2Fcontact_us.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=0cb27ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐黑警/撐送中黑店名單</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=17878867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Facebook page</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JiJqJK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JiJqJK&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=723ba516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JiJqJK</a><br />\n<br />\n補充表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/iRy1HizFPhpaGNt38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FiRy1HizFPhpaGNt38&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=fcab939a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/iRy1HizFPhpaGNt38</a>"},{"pid":"13f6678040eca86179948d2c74e0d12690cdb3c0","tid":1293814,"uid":260909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T21:34:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"885e0527fcfe4d081ca457bb74744807555080d6","tid":1293814,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:13:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid